  36:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/../stdlib/lv_string.h ****  * @return Pointer to the destination array.
  37:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/../stdlib/lv_string.h ****  * @note The function does not check for any overlapping of the source and destination memory block
  38:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/../stdlib/lv_string.h ****  */
